Comedian, Mr Macaroni, has expressed his fear of marriage and romantic relationships.



He made his stance known during a question and answer session on his Twitter handle on Wednesday.



When a fan asked if he was considering marriage anytime soon, the comedian said, “Noooooo!!!! Marriage scares me. I haven’t been in a relationship since my time in HNAUB (Houdegbe North America University, Cotonou. That’s like 2011-2012.”

